<p class="header noPspace">Onsite Groups</p>
<p class="sectionHeader noPspace normal">Every year about 500 people choose to do journey groups at a Crossroads campus site. <span style="line-height: 1.75;">Childcare provided at Florence and Oakley only.</span></p>
<p class="noPspace normal">If you&rsquo;re interested in hosting an onsite group, email host@crossroads.net&nbsp;with site and also names and ages of any kids needing childcare.&nbsp;</p>
<p class="noPspace normal">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="noPspace"><strong>FLORENCE</strong></p>
<p class="noPspace">Thursdays beginning 10/17, 7-8:45pm (Hosts arrive at 6pm for dinner.)</p>
<p class="noPspace">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="noPspace"><strong>MASON </strong></p>
<p class="noPspace">Thursdays beginning 10/17, 7-8:45pm (Hosts arrive at 6pm for dinner.).&nbsp;<em>Note&ndash;All Mason groups (including HS) will be meeting on Wednesday, October 30 at 7pm since Halloween falls on a Thursday.&nbsp;</em></p>
<p class="noPspace">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="noPspace"><strong>OAKLEY </strong></p>
<p class="noPspace">Tuesdays beginning 10/15, 7-8:45pm (Hosts arrive at 6pm for dinner.)</p>